  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  men and women

          -  over 18 years of age

          -  chronic liver disease

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe hepatic encephalopathy (CFF &lt;35 Hz)

          -  Interferon treatment

          -  hypercalcaemia (&gt;2.7 mmol/l) or hypercalciuria (&gt;8.0 mmol/d) with or without
             hyperparathyroidism (&gt;65.0 pg/ml)

          -  history of calcium-containing kidney stones

          -  allergy or hypersensitivity to any of the supplement ingredients: peanuts, soy,
             gelatin

          -  sarcoidosis

          -  stage IV or V Chronic Kidney Disease

          -  Pregnancy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
